    "description": "<p><strong>AFFLICTION (debilitating ray)</strong></p><p>A shooting attack with base damage 3, range 0/1. The attack does not inflict any actual damage – instead, if it penetrates any armor, the target suffers –3 dice to all attribute rolls until a <strong>PRESENCE</strong> roll (with the penalty) is made to shake off the effect. The <strong>PRESENCE</strong> roll is no action, but only one attempt can be made per round and only on the victim’s own turn.</p>",
